{"tid":1518160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[輿論戰] 晴報個投票收左皮，文匯報：唯有自己搞個投票","createTime":"2019-08-30T07:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T17:34:56.000Z","uid":73507,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"10bea69f8f01781f3e8d82ade64deeb7a4980618","tid":1518160,"uid":73507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:07:30.000Z","msg":"之前講過文匯報會成日拎經濟報x晴報個民調結果打J玩數字遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />六百人投票就已經代表左七成香港人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UZFO9mt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUZFO9mt.png&h=3360e733&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2019/06/19/HK1906190006.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2019%2F06%2F19%2FHK1906190006.htm&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUimAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=11c9a7ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2019/06/19/HK1906190006.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n但係呢幾個月輿論戰手足打得好好，基本上依家有新投票已經俾手足mon 住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ebe4LUj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEbe4LUj.jpg&h=2b213eb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/lifestyle/voting.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Flifestyle%2Fvoting.php&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUimAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=fc2a3eb8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/lifestyle/voting.php</a><br />\n依家晴報無數交<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />文匯唯有自己搞個垃圾投票做數寫下文啦<br />\n<br />\n有無輿論戰手足繼續一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://survey.wenweipo.com/survey.php?survey=1720\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsurvey.wenweipo.com%2Fsurvey.php%3Fsurvey%3D